  ${
    $d F j $.  $d F k $.  $d F x $.  $d j k $.  $d j x $.  $d k x $.  $d N k $.
    $d n k $.  $d N n $.  $d j n $.
    trireciplem.1 $e |- F = ( n e. NN |-> ( 1 / ( n x. ( n + 1 ) ) ) ) $.
    $( Lemma for ~ trirecip .  Show that the sum converges.  (Contributed by
       Scott Fenton, 22-Apr-2014.)  (Revised by Mario Carneiro,
       22-May-2014.) $)
    trireciplem $p |- seq 1 ( + , F ) ~~> 1 $=
