      wne nnne0 divsubdir pncan2 sylancl opreq1d mulid1 mulcom opreq12d divcan5
      syl112anc syl122anc eqtr3d 3eqtr3d sumeq2dv syl6eq cuz syl6eleq fsumtscop
      div1i simpr eqtrd id fsumser 3eqtr2rd climsubc2 trud subid1i breqtri ) EB
